  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Flesh Psychosis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Flesh Psychosis</i> is a calm puzzle game where you must match identical ingredients together to cook... special dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble ingredients to earn them in your inventory! Every 20 actions, a new cooking phase begins to find out if you are a good evil cook</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Madline discover even more dreadful recipes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >while achieving the best possible score! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use different actions each turn or drop new cursed foods to combine with others and add them to your inventory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware—if they fall into the funnel, they’ll be lost !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create terrifying recipes in your wicked kitchen !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10-15 different ingredients</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ different dishes to cook. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An infinite mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5+ hours of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small casual game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Flesh Psychosis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Flesh Psychosis</i> is a calm puzzle game where you must match identical ingredients together to cook... special dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble ingredients to earn them in your inventory! Every 20 actions, a new cooking phase begins to find out if you are a good evil cook</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Madline discover even more dreadful recipes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >while achieving the best possible score! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/c2486c01faf6ed03766e36ba0328b721.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use different actions each turn or drop new cursed foods to combine with others and add them to your inventory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware—if they fall into the funnel, they’ll be lost !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create terrifying recipes in your wicked kitchen !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.poster.avif?t=1753367661\" width=788 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.webm?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084720/extras/e5af96b6d0e53ae90b9244474750ae53.mp4?t=1753367661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10-15 different ingredients</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ different dishes to cook. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An infinite mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5+ hours of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small casual game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
